HEADWORD: Clearwing
<hw>Clear"wing`</hw> <pr>(kl⟦emac⟧r"w⟦icr⟧ng`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A lepidopterous insect with partially
